node.name: Travel-Tracker
node.description: The Travel Tracker website lets users mark countries they've visited on an interactive map, providing a visual record of their travels. Users can easily add, update, and manage their visited locations, with all data stored securely. The site offers a responsive, user-friendly experience for keeping track of travel history.

node.name: The_Simon_Game
node.description: Simon is a memory game with colored buttons. It shows a sequence of lights and sounds, and you have to copy it by pressing the buttons. The more you get right, the harder it gets. Mess up, and you start over. It's a fun challenge for your memory skills!

node.name: TO-DO-List
node.description: A simple to-do list web application where users can add, edit, and remove tasks.It provides an intuitive interface to manage tasks easily. Perfect for organizing daily activities efficiently.

node.name: Drum-Kit-Game
node.description: Drum Kit offers a virtual drumming experience with realistic sounds. Play using your keyboard or touch on any device. Perfect for music lovers of all levels to enjoy drumming anytime, anywhere!
